Which aspect of the study is considered experimental according to the consent form?
A) The use of the FDA-approved ExactVu device for micro-ultrasound imaging of the prostate;
B) The use of investigational software in conjunction with the ExactVu device;
C) The process of comparing ultrasound images with pathology reports;
D) The routine prostate biopsy or radical prostatectomy for prostate cancer treatment.

Correct answer: B
